    "summary": "crbonfree.com exposes one documented REST API at https://api.crbonfree.com with an OpenAPI spec, plus three package-delivered CLIs: the npm MCP CLI, npm SDK CLI, and Python CLI; all require CrbonFree-issued credentials.",
